flowchart TD
  A[Engineer prepares production release] --> B[npm run auth:config:check]
  B -->|no complete auth strategy| C[Fail before deployable build]
  B -->|OIDC selected and missing OIDC/JWKS config| C
  B -->|internal-bootstrap selected and missing secret or flags| C
  B -->|valid| D[Write non-secret auth diagnostics artifact]
  D --> E[npm run build]
  E --> F[npm run auth:config:check:vercel]
  F -->|missing env names for both strategies| G[Block release and notify production config owner]
  F -->|OIDC or internal-bootstrap names present| H[Trigger new production deployment]
  H --> I[Inspect Ready deployment, commit, timestamp]
  I --> J{Selected strategy}
  J -->|oidc| K[Verify /auth/callback redirect URI in IdP allowlist]
  J -->|internal-bootstrap| L[Verify approved auth-code issuance and secret rotation owner]
  K --> M[Operator runs production sign-in smoke]
  L --> M
  M --> N[Protected view loads data or intentional empty state]
  N --> P[Auth availability alerts monitor login path and callback failures]
  P --> Q[Issue remains production-remediation-pending until evidence is attached]
  C --> O[/sign-in shows no-login-path configuration state]
